<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AMINA Académie | Devenez Expert Comptable & CEO</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #4F46E5; /* Deep Indigo */
            --primary-hover: #4338CA;
            --accent: #F59E0B; /* Gold for premium feel */
            --bg-light: #F8FAFC;
            --text-main: #0F172A;
            --text-muted: #475569;
            --white: #FFFFFF;
        }

        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-light);
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* --- PREMIUM NAVBAR (Glassmorphism) --- */
        nav {
            padding: 18px 8%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }
        .logo {
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--text-main);
            text-decoration: none;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        .logo span { color: var(--primary); }
        
        .nav-links { display: flex; align-items: center; }
        .nav-links a {
            color: var(--text-main);
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-right: 25px;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 15px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--primary); }

        .btn-nav {
            background: var(--text-main);
            color: var(--white) !important;
            padding: 10px 22px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: 0.3s;
            margin-right: 0 !important;
        }
        .btn-nav:hover { background: var(--primary); transform: translateY(-2px); }

        /* Mobile Nav Fix */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            nav { padding: 15px 5%; }
            .nav-links a:not(.btn-nav) { display: none; } /* Hide text links on mobile */
        }

        /* --- HERO SECTION (Vercel Style) --- */
        .hero {
            padding: 120px 8% 100px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 50px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, #EEF2FF 0%, transparent 50%),
                        radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, #FFFBEB 0%, transparent 50%);
        }

        .hero-content { flex: 1; max-width: 650px; }
        
        .badge-pro {
            display: inline-block;
            background: rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.1);
            color: var(--primary);
            padding: 6px 16px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.2);
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
            font-size: 64px;
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1.1;
            letter-spacing: -2px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            color: var(--text-main);
        }
        .hero h1 span {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary), #818CF8);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 35px;
            font-weight: 400;
            max-width: 550px;
        }

        .hero-btns { display: flex; gap: 15px; align-items: center; }

        .btn-main {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            padding: 16px 35px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.3);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .btn-main:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.4); }
        
        .btn-sec {
            color: var(--text-main);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .btn-sec:hover { color: var(--primary); }

        .hero-img-box { flex: 1; position: relative; }
        .hero-img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
            border: 8px solid white;
            transform: perspective(1000px) rotateY(-5deg);
            transition: 0.5s;
        }
        .hero-img:hover { transform: perspective(1000px) rotateY(0deg); }

        .float-badge {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -20px;
            left: -30px;
            background: white;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
            z-index: 10;
        }
        .float-badge span { font-size: 24px; }
        .float-badge div p { margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); }
        .float-badge div h4 { margin: 0; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800; }

        /* Hero Responsive Fix */
        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .hero { padding: 80px 5% 60px; flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
            .hero-content { max-width: 100%; }
            .hero h1 { font-size: 42px; letter-spacing: -1px; }
            .hero p { font-size: 18px; margin: 0 auto 30px; }
            .hero-btns { justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
            .hero-img-box { width: 100%; max-width: 500px; margin-top: 40px; }
            .hero-img { transform: none; }
            .float-badge { left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); bottom: -20px; width: max-content; }
        }

        /* --- THE EMPIRE BLUEPRINT (Features) --- */
        .blueprint-section {
            padding: 80px 8%;
            background: white;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .blueprint-section h2 {
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
            font-size: 40px;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }
        .blueprint-section p.sub {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 18px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto 50px;
        }

        .course-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .card {
            background: var(--bg-light);
            padding: 40px 30px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #E2E8F0;
            transition: 0.3s;
            position: relative;
        }
        .card:hover {
            background: white;
            border-color: var(--primary);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
        .icon-box {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 16px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }
        .card h3 { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        .card p { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 15px; }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .blueprint-section { padding: 60px 5%; }
            .blueprint-section h2 { font-size: 30px; }
            .course-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }

        /* --- TESTIMONIALS SECTION --- */
        .testimonials {
            padding: 100px 8%;
            background: var(--bg-light);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .testimonials h2 {
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
            font-size: 40px;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            color: var(--text-main);
            letter-spacing: -1px;
        }
        .testi-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .testi-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.03);
            border: 1px solid #E2E8F0;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .testi-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            border-color: var(--primary);
        }
        .stars { color: #F59E0B; font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; letter-spacing: 2px;}
        .testi-text { font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-muted); font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 25px; line-height: 1.7; }
        .testi-user { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px; }
        .testi-avatar { width: 55px; height: 55px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; border: 2px solid #E2E8F0;}
        .user-info h4 { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-main); margin-bottom: 2px;}
        .user-info p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-muted); margin: 0; }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .testimonials { padding: 60px 5%; }
            .testimonials h2 { font-size: 30px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
            .testi-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }

        /* --- CTA SECTION --- */
        .cta-section {
            padding: 100px 8%;
            background: var(--text-main);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .cta-section h2 {
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .cta-section p { font-size: 20px; color: #94A3B8; margin-bottom: 40px; max-width: 600px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;}
        .btn-cta {
            background: var(--accent);
            color: var(--text-main);
            padding: 18px 40px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 800;
            text-decoration: none;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.4);
            transition: 0.3s;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .btn-cta:hover { transform: scale(1.05); background: #FCD34D; }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .cta-section { padding: 60px 5%; }
            .cta-section h2 { font-size: 32px; }
            .cta-section p { font-size: 16px; }
            .btn-cta { padding: 15px 30px; font-size: 16px; width: 100%; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <a href="/" class="logo">AMINA <span>Académie</span></a>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="#programme">Le Programme</a>
            <a href="#temoignages">Témoignages</a>
            <a href="/login">Se connecter</a>
            <a href="/register" class="btn-nav">Rejoindre l'élite</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <div class="badge-pro">🚀 Niveau Pro Max Disponible</div>
            <h1>Devenez un Expert, Bâtissez un <span>Empire.</span></h1>
            <p>Bien plus qu'un cours de comptabilité. Un système complet pour maîtriser la gestion, acquérir des clients et automatiser vos revenus au Maroc.</p>
            
            <div class="hero-btns">
                <a href="/register" class="btn-main">Accéder au Système (40 Leçons)</a>
                <a href="#programme" class="btn-sec">Voir le programme ↓</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-img-box">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1460925895917-afdab827c52f?q=80&w=1000&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Dashboard Setup" class="hero-img">
            <div class="float-badge">
                <span>🏆</span>
                <div>
                    <h4>100% Pratique</h4>
                    <p>Conforme DGI & PCM</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="programme" class="blueprint-section">
        <h2>Le "Ultimate Blueprint"</h2>
        <p class="sub">Notre méthode en 4 piliers pour passer de zéro à un système automatisé générant des revenus.</p>

        <div class="course-grid">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="icon-box">🧠</div>
                <h3>1. Fondation & Skills</h3>
                <p>Maîtrisez le Plan Comptable Marocain, le CPC, la TVA et les écritures comptables comme un chef comptable.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="icon-box">💻</div>
                <h3>2. Logiciels & Pratique</h3>
                <p>Traitez des dossiers réels sur Sage, gérez la paie (CNSS) et faites des télédéclarations en direct.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="icon-box">🤝</div>
                <h3>3. Acquisition Client</h3>
                <p>Apprenez à construire une marque personnelle forte, trouver des clients B2B et clore des contrats High-Ticket.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="icon-box">⚙️</div>
                <h3>4. Automatisation</h3>
                <p>Ne travaillez plus pour l'argent. Créez des systèmes, déléguez et scalez votre agence ou freelance.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="temoignages" class="testimonials">
        <h2>Ils ont bâti leur empire 👑</h2>
        <div class="testi-grid">
            
            <div class="testi-card">
                <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p class="testi-text">"Avant AMINA Académie, je ne comprenais rien à la TVA ni aux déclarations. Aujourd'hui, je gère 5 clients en freelance grâce aux systèmes d'automatisation enseignés. Un investissement rentabilisé en 1 mois !"</p>
                <div class="testi-user">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?q=80&w=200&auto=format&fit=crop" class="testi-avatar" alt="User">
                    <div class="user-info">
                        <h4>Karim B.</h4>
                        <p>Comptable Indépendant</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="testi-card">
                <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p class="testi-text">"Le module sur l'acquisition de clients High-Ticket a tout changé. Je suis passé de simples saisies comptables à la vente de packages complets de conseil financier. La qualité des leçons est digne d'un Master."</p>
                <div class="testi-user">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108377-be9c29b29330?q=80&w=200&auto=format&fit=crop" class="testi-avatar" alt="User">
                    <div class="user-info">
                        <h4>Nadia M.</h4>
                        <p>Fondatrice d'Agence</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="testi-card">
                <div class="stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p class="testi-text">"J'adore le simulateur FIFO et les zones de pratique à la fin de cada leccion. Ce n'est pas juste de la théorie ennuyeuse, c'est de l'action pure. L'interface est magnifique et super motivante."</p>
                <div class="testi-user">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519085360753-af0119f7cbe7?q=80&w=200&auto=format&fit=crop" class="testi-avatar" alt="User">
                    <div class="user-info">
                        <h4>Youssef T.</h4>
                        <p>Étudiant Expert-Comptable</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
        <h2>Prêt à changer votre trajectoire ?</h2>
        <p>Rejoignez AMINA Académie aujourd'hui et commencez à construire votre liberté financière.</p>
        <a href="/register" class="btn-cta">Créer mon compte maintenant ➔</a>
    </section>

</body>
</html>